cscie97.asn3.housemate.model

Class Status

  • java.lang.Object
    • cscie97.asn3.knowledge.engine.Node
      • cscie97.asn3.housemate.model.HouseMateNode
        • cscie97.asn3.housemate.model.Status

  • public class Status
extends HouseMateNode
    Status follows the Strategy pattern for the option behaviors. This allows for Statuses to have different validation for their values. The behaviors can be configured via the set options command.
